VACATION TO THE BAHAMAS.

40:23.750 --> 40:25.458
I DON'T REALLY KNOW
WHAT CAME OVER ME.

40:25.458 --> 40:27.917
YEAH, UM,
ME NEITHER.

40:27.917 --> 40:29.792
