THE METHOD.

40:29.792 --> 40:33.250
I'VE BEEN WATCHING
A LOT OF JAMES LIPTON LATELY.

40:33.250 --> 40:34.667
YEAH.
THAT MUST BE IT,

40:34.667 --> 40:36.834
BECAUSE, YOU KNOW,
NOW THAT WE HAVE
HER PERMISSION,

40:36.834 --> 40:38.250
THE FEELING
IS JUST--

