THAT YOU DO.

41:38.792 --> 41:40.417
HOW DO YOU DO
THAT THING?

41:40.417 --> 41:41.667
WHAT THING?

41:41.667 --> 41:44.750
YOU SMILE
AND THE WHOLE WORLD
LIGHTS UP.

41:46.000 --> 41:48.000
ACTING.

41:48.000 --> 41:49.834
HMM. BEATS THE HELL
OUTTA WORK.

42:14.333 --> 42:16.500
