42:16.500 --> 42:18.000
BOTTOM OF THE NINTH,
BASES LOADED,

42:18.000 --> 42:21.125
SAMMY....SOMETHING
IS UP TO BAT.

42:21.125 --> 42:23.000
POTTER'S ONE LAST SHOT
AT IMMORTALITY.

42:23.000 --> 42:25.208
THE WINDUP, THE PITCH.

42:25.208 --> 42:26.708
YAAAH!

42:26.708 --> 42:29.166
AND THE CROWD GOES WILD!
